OL,3,CFamily of father who spent final days
OL,4,Cin hospice say 'it needs to stay open'
OL,6,FHis wife Pippa said: "Even an hour
OL,7,Fbefore he died, he was eating an
OL,8,Fomelette! That's simply down to how
OL,9,Fincredible everyone at the hospice
OL,10,Fwas. I am eternally grateful to every
OL,11,Fsingle person at Trinity. I don't know
OL,12,Fhow we would have coped on our own."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
