OL,3,CFamily of father who spent final days
OL,4,Cin hospice say 'it needs to stay open'
OL,6,F"It's like all of a sudden someone
OL,7,Ftakes your hand and says, 'it's going
OL,8,Fto be OK', and you realise it will be
OL,9,FOK. The day is coming, and it'll be
OL,10,Fsad, but you're in this perfect place,
OL,11,Fyou're all together and it's peaceful.
OL,12,FAt Trinity, this heartbreaking moment
OL,13,Fis also calm and as pleasant an
OL,14,Fexperience as it possibly can be."
