OL,3,CFamily of father who spent final days
OL,4,Cin hospice say 'it needs to stay open'
OL,6,FTrinity Hospice provides free quality
OL,7,Fend of life care to patients across
OL,8,Fthe Fylde Coast, but as costs for
OL,9,Feveryday items as well as medical
OL,10,Fequipment increases, the hospice is
OL,11,Ffacing tough decisions about
OL,12,Fpotentially cutting services.
OL,14,FSteve's family are backing a national
OL,15,Fcampaign calling on more people to
OL,16,Fleave money in their wills to
OL,17,Fhospices, allowing them to provide
OL,18,Fquality end of life care."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
