OL,3,CFamily of father who spent final days
OL,4,Cin hospice say 'it needs to stay open'
OL,6,FDavid Houston, Chief Executive at
OL,7,FTrinity, said: "As a registered
OL,8,Fcharity, we rely heavily on donations
OL,9,Fto keep our doors open. That's why
OL,10,Fwe've joined forces to shine a light
OL,11,Fon the essential role hospices play in
OL,12,Four communities
OL,14,Fand protect our futures."
OL,16,FThe operating costs for Trinity
OL,17,FHospice are just over #14 million, but
OL,18,Fwith the organisation projected to be
OL,19,Frunning at a loss in 2025, David says
OL,20,Fdonations are now more important than
OL,21,Fever.
