OL,3,CFamily of father who spent final days
OL,4,Cin hospice say 'it needs to stay open'
OL,6,FHe said: "Hospices can make a big
OL,7,Fdifference, we can help get people out
OL,8,Fof hospital and give them the death
OL,9,Fthey deserve... but I can't guarantee
OL,10,Fthat in the way that I could a few
OL,11,Fyears ago."
OL,13,FFor Steve's family, the care he
OL,14,Freceived meant they could enjoy their
OL,15,Ffinal few months together.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
